dynamic type.

00:10:41.516 --> 00:10:43.776 A:middle
So, I hope to see you all at

00:10:44.616 --> 00:10:46.206 A:middle
these sessions.

00:10:46.866 --> 00:10:48.826 A:middle
Moving on, we have the

00:10:48.826 --> 00:10:50.466 A:middle
Accessibility keyboard.

00:10:51.286 --> 00:10:52.826 A:middle
This is a feature built for

00:10:52.826 --> 00:10:55.466 A:middle
macOS for users who have enough

00:10:55.466 --> 00:10:58.186 A:middle
