00:11:42.926 --> 00:11:44.496 A:middle
feature allows you to interact

00:11:44.496 --> 00:11:46.796 A:middle
with Siri via text input like

00:11:46.796 --> 00:11:48.456 A:middle
you would via speech.

00:11:48.886 --> 00:11:50.396 A:middle
