00:15:38.306 --> 00:15:41.746 A:middle
Now we have a tool called the

00:15:41.746 --> 00:15:43.656 A:middle
Accessibility Inspector that can

00:15:43.656 --> 00:15:45.456 A:middle
also be used for auditing your

00:15:46.306 --> 00:15:46.416 A:middle
apps.

